  "body": "**üßê Motivation**\r\n<!-- Is your feature request related to a specific problem? Is it just a crazy idea? Tell us about it! -->\r\n\r\nThere is a number of games with gene sequences mechanism like CryptoKitties, DeRace, and Axie. Imagine I have a Kitty with rare genes and I want to breed it with others for profit. There is no easy way of doing so because all games have different interfaces and thus It is difficult for exchanges to implement lend/borrow mechanics. ERC4907 will standardize the way how it is done without implementing a flash-borrower and magic tricks\r\n\r\n**üìù Details**\r\n<!-- Please describe your feature request in detail. -->\r\nHere is ready to use implementation\r\nhttps://thirdweb.com/doubledev.eth/ERC4907\r\n\r\n<!-- Make sure that you have reviewed the OpenZeppelin Contracts Contributor Guidelines. -->\r\n<!-- https://github.com/OpenZeppelin/openzeppelin-contracts/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md -->\r\n",
